OpenLDAP Software is a free, open source implementation of the Lightweight Directory Access Protocol (LDAP) developed by the OpenLDAP Project. Using a client/server architecture, LDAP provides reliable means to create a central information directory accessible from the network.LDAP organizes information in a hierarchical manner using directories.LDAP is commonly used for centrally managed users and groups, user authentication, or system configuration.This solution provides automated installation and configuration for OpenLDAP(Standalone Configuration) as a service. 